heading: Iron Hold Dungeon Guide
content: Iron Hold does not contain any dangerous monsters, but has a convoluted layout that requires a great deal of backtracking. This dungeon has decent density, and is currently a possible . Scourge of the Land is an easy meat piñata boss. This dungeon unlocks the , a near useless aspect meant for a Necromancer. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
